thread.title: At least 10 youths missing in Israel flash flood

title: At least 10 youths missing in Israel flash flood
text:
At least 10 youths missing in Israel flash flood 6:54pm BST - 00:47
At least 10 youths were missing after they were swept away by a flash flood in the Negev Desert in southern Israel on Thursday, and seven others were in critical condition, police and emergency services said. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
